
This is HTML::Selector::XPath::Simple, which is a simple utility to
access XML/HTML elements by using CSS selector.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

HTML::Selector::XPath
HTML::TreeBuilder::XPath


